<Base title="Current RMS Integrations — DH7" description="Custom integrations for Current RMS. Connect your rental management system to accounting, CRM, and communication tools in real time.">
  <h1>Current RMS Integrations</h1>

  <p>Current RMS handles a lot. But it doesn't handle everything — and what sits outside it, your accounting package, your CRM, your communication tools, still needs to stay in sync.</p>

  <p>We build integrations that connect Current RMS to the rest of your stack.</p>

  <h2>Opportunities</h2>

  <p>When a new opportunity lands in Current RMS, your wider team needs to know. We can push new and updated opportunities to your CRM, trigger notifications in Slack or Teams, or feed a shared pipeline view — so nothing falls through the gap between systems.</p>

  <h2>Invoices</h2>

  <p>Chasing invoice status across two systems is wasted time. We sync invoices between Current RMS and your accounting package — Xero, QuickBooks, or others — so payment status is current in both places without anyone touching it.</p>

  <h2>Contacts</h2>

  <p>Contacts created or updated in Current RMS can flow to your CRM automatically. Contacts acquired elsewhere can flow back in. One source of truth, maintained without manual effort.</p>

  <h2>Real-time</h2>

  <p>Batch syncs introduce lag. A contact updated at 9am might not appear elsewhere until noon. We build event-driven integrations using Current RMS webhooks, so changes propagate in seconds, not hours. Your data is current because it has to be.</p>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>Tell us your current stack and where the friction is. We'll scope what's possible and build it.</p>
  <p><a href="mailto:damien@26brains.com">damien@26brains.com</a></p>
</Base>
